➜【泰国示威】警方下令关闭空铁及地铁线 无碍大批示威者上街
http://dwnews.com/-/60215401	38761
<div><div><p>下图为五岔路口叻抛站大批示威者挤满街头的情形泰国曼谷数以千计示威者不理政府已发发布紧急命令，10月17日上街示威。即使警方已封闭市内两大路口、有BTS及MRT线路应警方要求关闭，亦无阻人们参与抗议。</p></div><p>警方首次于这一波示威中动用水炮驱散人群翌日，组织示威的人说会在下午16时举行集会，但未有透露地点，至稍后时间才有消息传出，集会地点定在五岔路口叻抛站（BTS-Ha Yaek Lat Phrao）、乌东素站（BTS-Udomsuk）及翁怀亚站（BTS-Wongwian Yai）。</p><p><strong>↓想看10月17日的曼谷多处示威现场图片，请点击放大观看：</strong></p><div><div><div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div></div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div></div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div></div><div><div><div><div></div></div></div></div><div><div><div><div></div><div><div>+<!-- -->9</div></div></div></div></div><div><div><div><div></div><div><div>+<!-- -->8</div></div></div></div></div><div><div><div><div></div><div><div>+<!-- -->7</div></div></div></div></div></div><p>除了有数以千示威者来到位于曼谷北部的五岔路口叻抛站。市内一些地方都有示威活动。有人高叫巴育下台的口号。</p><p><strong>下图为五岔路口叻抛站大批示威者挤满街头的情形：</strong></p><div><div><blockquote><p lang="en" dir="ltr">The scene at Lat Phrao in Bangkok as thousands of Thais join anti-government protests in defiance of a ban with more joining all the time. This is just one location. It&#39;s happening elsewhere too. <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%9A17%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%B8%E0%B8%A5%E0%B8%B2?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#ม็อบ17ตุลา</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/WhatsHappeningInThailand?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#WhatsHappeningInThailand</a> via <a href="https://twitter.com/Athit_P?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Athit_P</a> <a href="https://t.co/S6OqbFjQ6S">pic.twitter.com/S6OqbFjQ6S</a></p>&mdash; Matthew Tostevin (@TostevinM) <a href="https://twitter.com/TostevinM/status/1317391705084100610?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 17, 2020</a></blockquote> </div></div><p><strong>↓下图为翁怀亚站的示威者，部分人拿起字段，似乎准备架起路障：</strong></p><div><div><blockquote><p lang="en" dir="ltr">A new protest site has emerged at BTS Wongwian Yai with protesters taking the area. <br><br>Many areas of Bangkok now filled with protesters! <a href="https:/